.PS
scale=2.54
CROSS: box invis "$RW \[mu] RW$"
POLLEN1: box invis "$R$" with .ne at CROSS.s
POLLEN2: box invis "$W$" with .nw at CROSS.s
"Pollen" with .nw at POLLEN1.nw
B11: box fill 0.2 "$1 smallover 4 RR$" with .ne at POLLEN1.se
B12: box fill 0.2 "$1 smallover 4 RW$" with .nw at POLLEN2.sw
B21: box fill 0.2 "$1 smallover 4 WR$" with .ne at B11.se
B22: box "$1 smallover 4 WW$" with .nw at B12.sw
OVULE1: box invis "$R$" with .e at B11.w
OVULE2: box invis "$W$" with .e at B21.w
"Ovules" with .nw at OVULE1.nw
.PE
